WEBVTT

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:01.076
Si, cawn/ilak ding taktak 
kan hrialh sual kho men.

00:02:01.100 --> 00:02:02.976
Abiapibik kan cawn hnga dingmi--

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.521
na hngalh kho maw?--

00:02:04.545 --> 00:02:06.976
cu thithruainak cu thangthatnak asi.

00:02:07.729 --> 00:02:09.777
Asi, a thawk hmasatu cu angki hruklopa asi

00:02:09.801 --> 00:02:11.310
i amah cu lawmh asi ko lai,

00:02:11.334 --> 00:02:13.124
nain zulhtu hna nunthlentu taktak cu

00:02:13.148 --> 00:02:15.976
zultu hmasa khi dakaw asi.

00:02:16.488 --> 00:02:18.739
i, hruaitu kan si dih aherh
timi cawnpiaknak hi

00:02:18.763 --> 00:02:20.355
sullam a ngeih tuk then lai lo.

00:02:20.379 --> 00:02:22.783
Cawlcanghnak thawk
nai timh taktak ahcun

00:02:22.807 --> 00:02:25.976
zulh ding ralthatnak ngei law,
zulhning zong cawnpiak hna.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.614
Cun, santlailo nih thiltha 
pakhatkhat an tuah ahcun,

00:02:28.638 --> 00:02:31.976
zultu tha ah ser khawh izuam colh.